        Parameters:
        index - Indicates the index (0-based) of the cell List to sort on.
        direction - Indicates the direction of the sort: "asc" or "desc". If not one of these two values, then defaults to "asc".
        sortType - Indicates the type of sort to perform: SORT_TYPE_STRING or SORT_TYPE_NUMBER.
